s/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你會希望佢冇表白到定照表白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寧願無表講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能未表之前大家都覺得係more than friend 但又未到要一齊<br />\n表左之後依家佢好似唔想再理我 好似無存在過咁<br />\n會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fee92133f3ec301f885405fe4e5b7f24667353a","tid":284223,"uid":44336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n叫個 好鼓勵  好關心 自己的姐姐<br />\n唔 好再搵自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁岩既巴打 我果陣都係咁 有個對我好好既姐姐<br />\n又係好關心自己 但係最後見我都係一pat屎咁<br />\n所以無理到我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d068cbe49714ce0e7a31991f5aa515576ec07a4","tid":284223,"uid":123059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>timing唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細識到大 偏偏係我想同佢一齊嘅時候 佢無反應<br />\n到佢表白話想一齊嘅時候 其實我已經一早睇淡唸住做一世好朋友 再無想一齊嘅感覺<br />\n到最後  連好朋友都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你會希望佢冇表白到定照表白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寧願無表講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能未表之前大家都覺得係more than friend 但又未到要一齊<br />\n表左之後依家佢好似唔想再理我 好似無存在過咁<br />\n會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我好想同被表白個女仔講 我真係好想好似以前咁<br />\n但依刻我真係唔知點 好怕煩到妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b27df4a78e12c4fe2938e69b86b601e231e7db","tid":284223,"uid":5340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"我有"},{"pid":"0f6c75f8dd971cd8d8012500bd903797fa0715ce","tid":284223,"uid":23613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquo